function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

-- Enable spawners
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tSpawners) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
		end
	end
	
	
end

function Start(szGroup)

--Enable the bonus chest.
Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(ID_BONUS_CHEST, false)

end

function Start()
	
--Destroy any remainnig walls.	
	local tWalls = Hydra.ActorsInGroup(S_WALL_ACTOR_GROUP)
	
	for i, idWall in ipairs(tWalls) do
		Hydra.QActorWait(idWall, Hydra.GetRandomFloat())
		Hydra.QActorKill(idWall)
	end
	
--Disable spawners.	
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tSpawners) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, true)
		end
	end
	
end
